# prefix-block-duplicate-keys

## Input

```
item. {
  tag a
  tag b
}

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..26
  PREFIX_BLOCK@0..26
    WORD_KEY@0..5
      WORD@0..5 "item."
    SPACE@5..6 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@6..7 "{"
    NEWLINE@7..8 "\n"
    SPACE@8..10 "  "
    ENTRY@10..16
      WORD_KEY@10..13
        WORD@10..13 "tag"
      SPACE@13..14 " "
      LINE_STRING@14..15
        STRING@14..15 "a"
      NEWLINE@15..16 "\n"
    SPACE@16..18 "  "
    ENTRY@18..24
      WORD_KEY@18..21
        WORD@18..21 "tag"
      SPACE@21..22 " "
      LINE_STRING@22..23
        STRING@22..23 "b"
      NEWLINE@23..24 "\n"
    CLOSE_BRACE@24..25 "}"
    NEWLINE@25..26 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        PrefixBlock {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..5 "item.",
            },
            open_brace: OPEN_BRACE@6..7 "{",
            items: [
                Entry {
                    key: WordKey {
                        word: WORD@10..13 "tag",
                    },
                    value: LineString {
                        string: STRING@14..15 "a",
                    },
                },
                Entry {
                    key: WordKey {
                        word: WORD@18..21 "tag",
                    },
                    value: LineString {
                        string: STRING@22..23 "b",
                    },
                },
            ],
            close_brace: CLOSE_BRACE@24..25 "}",
        },
    ],
}
```

